{"id":90611,"title":"Healing, healthcare, missions, the church.","abstract":"Churches throughout history have modeled ministry on Jesus' life of reaching out, teaching, preaching, and healing. Kampala Baptist Church (KBC) in Uganda is one such church that works to care spiritually and physically for their community. Partnering with local healthcare providers and short- and long-term healthcare missionaries, the church is transforming lives. Read about KBC and explore healthcare missions ministry.","date":"2014-03-05","categories":"Wounds and Injuries","split":"test","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24592600","annotations":[{"name":"Jesus","weight":0.804197,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jesus"},{"name":"Missionary","weight":0.801843,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Missionary"},{"name":"Health care","weight":0.746519,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health_care"},{"name":"Baptists","weight":0.734391,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Baptists"},{"name":"Church (building)","weight":0.678452,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Church_(building)"},{"name":"History","weight":0.646869,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/History"},{"name":"Mission (Christianity)","weight":0.611248,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mission_(Christianity)"},{"name":"Sermon","weight":0.605027,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sermon"},{"name":"Education","weight":0.583977,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Education"},{"name":"Uganda","weight":0.554984,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Uganda"},{"name":"Community","weight":0.426731,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Community"},{"name":"Catholic Church","weight":0.305245,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Catholic_Church"},{"name":"Christian ministry","weight":0.264181,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Christian_ministry"},{"name":